    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hand tools used for making holes in sheet materials, particularly leather. These consist of dual jaws, one fitted with a hollow punch and the other a flat die against which the punch presses.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
